<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.4.10">
<l>viṇṇiṉmī tamararkaḷ virumpit toḻa</l>
<l rend="indent">miṟaittāyar pāṭiyil vīti yūṭē</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṅkā lippiṉṉē yeḻunta ruḷak</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṇṭiḷa vāykkaṉṉi mārkā muṟṟa</l>
<l>vaṇṇamvaṇ ṭamarpoḻil putuvai yarkōṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">viṭṭucit taṉcoṉṉa mālai pattum</l>
<l>paṇṇiṉpam varappāṭum patta ruḷḷār</l>
<l rend="indent">paramāṉa vaikuntam naṇṇu varē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are devotees who joyfully sing in melodies</l>
<l>[this] garland of ten [verses] composed by Viṭṭucittaṉ,</l>
<l>king of those of Putuvai with groves where bees dwell,</l>
<l rend="indent">about the way that the young maidens experienced desire</l>
<l rend="indent">[upon] seeing Kaṇṇaṉ appear behind the herd of cows</l>
<l rend="indent">in the middle of the street in the herder village</l>
<l rend="indent">in order to grace [them],</l>
<l rend="indent">[while] the celestials in the highest heavens toil</l>
<l rend="indent">to worship [him] intensely,</l>
<l>they will reach highest Vaikunta!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
